3494 return JSValue();
3495 }
3496 return m_gcBuffer.at(index);
3497 }
3498 case MessagePortReferenceTag: {
3499 uint32_t index;
3500 bool indexSuccessfullyRead = read(index);
3501 if (!indexSuccessfullyRead || index >= m_messagePorts.size()) {
3502 fail();
3503 return JSValue();
3504 }
3505 return getJSValue(m_messagePorts[index].get());
3506 }
3507#if ENABLE(WEBASSEMBLY)
3508 case WasmModuleTag: {
3509 uint32_t index;
3510 bool indexSuccessfullyRead = read(index);
3511 if (!indexSuccessfullyRead || !m_wasmModules || index >= m_wasmModules->size()) {
3512 fail();
3513 return JSValue();
3514 }
3515 auto scope = DECLARE_THROW_SCOPE(m_lexicalGlobalObject->vm());
3516 JSValue result = JSC::JSWebAssemblyModule::createStub(m_lexicalGlobalObject->vm(), m_lexicalGlobalObject, m_globalObject->webAssemblyModuleStructure(), m_wasmModules->at(index));
3517 // Since we are cloning a JSWebAssemblyModule, it's impossible for that
3518 // module to not have been a valid module. Therefore, createStub should
3519 // not throw.
3520 scope.releaseAssertNoException();
3521 m_gcBuffer.appendWithCrashOnOverflow(result);
3522 return result;
3523 }
3524 case WasmMemoryTag: {
3525 uint32_t index;
3526 bool indexSuccessfullyRead = read(index);
3527 if (!indexSuccessfullyRead || !m_wasmMemoryHandles || index >= m_wasmMemoryHandles->size()) {
3528 fail();
3529 return JSValue();
3530 }
3531 RefPtr<Wasm::MemoryHandle> handle = m_wasmMemoryHandles->at(index);
3532 if (!handle) {
3533 fail();
3534 return JSValue();
3535 }
3536 auto& vm = m_lexicalGlobalObject->vm();
3537 auto scope = DECLARE_THROW_SCOPE(vm);
3538 JSWebAssemblyMemory* result = JSC::JSWebAssemblyMemory::tryCreate(m_lexicalGlobalObject, vm, m_globalObject->webAssemblyMemoryStructure());
3539 // Since we are cloning a JSWebAssemblyMemory, it's impossible for that
3540 // module to not have been a valid module. Therefore, createStub should
3541 // not throw.
3542 scope.releaseAssertNoException();
3543 Ref<Wasm::Memory> memory = Wasm::Memory::create(handle.releaseNonNull(),
3544 [&vm] (Wasm::Memory::NotifyPressure) { vm.heap.collectAsync(CollectionScope::Full); },
3545 [&vm] (Wasm::Memory::SyncTryToReclaim) { vm.heap.collectSync(CollectionScope::Full); },
3546 [&vm, result] (Wasm::Memory::GrowSuccess, Wasm::PageCount oldPageCount, Wasm::PageCount newPageCount) { result->growSuccessCallback(vm, oldPageCount, newPageCount); });
3547 result->adopt(WTFMove(memory));
3548 m_gcBuffer.appendWithCrashOnOverflow(result);
3549 return result;
3550 }
3551#endif
3552 case ArrayBufferTag: {
3553 RefPtr<ArrayBuffer> arrayBuffer;
3554 if (!readArrayBuffer(arrayBuffer)) {
3555 fail();
3556 return JSValue();
3557 }
3558 Structure* structure = m_globalObject->arrayBufferStructure(arrayBuffer->sharingMode());
3559 // A crazy RuntimeFlags mismatch could mean that we are not equipped to handle shared
3560 // array buffers while the sender is. In that case, we would see a null structure here.
3561 if (!structure) {
3562 fail();
3563 return JSValue();
3564 }
3565 JSValue result = JSArrayBuffer::create(m_lexicalGlobalObject->vm(), structure, WTFMove(arrayBuffer));
3566 m_gcBuffer.appendWithCrashOnOverflow(result);
3567 return result;
3568 }
3569 case ArrayBufferTransferTag: {
3570 uint32_t index;
3571 bool indexSuccessfullyRead = read(index);
3572 if (!indexSuccessfullyRead || index >= m_arrayBuffers.size()) {
3573 fail();
3574 return JSValue();
3575 }
3576
3577 if (!m_arrayBuffers[index])
3578 m_arrayBuffers[index] = ArrayBuffer::create(WTFMove(m_arrayBufferContents->at(index)));
3579
3580 return getJSValue(m_arrayBuffers[index].get());
3581 }
3582 case SharedArrayBufferTag: {
3583 uint32_t index = UINT_MAX;
3584 bool indexSuccessfullyRead = read(index);
3585 if (!indexSuccessfullyRead || !m_sharedBuffers || index >= m_sharedBuffers->size()) {
3586 fail();
3587 return JSValue();
3588 }
3589
3590 RELEASE_ASSERT(m_sharedBuffers->at(index));
3591 auto buffer = ArrayBuffer::create(WTFMove(m_sharedBuffers->at(index)));
3592 JSValue result = getJSValue(buffer.get());
3593 m_gcBuffer.appendWithCrashOnOverflow(result);
3594 return result;
3595 }
3596 case ArrayBufferViewTag: {
3597 JSValue arrayBufferView;
3598 if (!readArrayBufferView(m_lexicalGlobalObject->vm(), arrayBufferView)) {
3599 fail();
3600 return JSValue();
3601 }
3602 m_gcBuffer.appendWithCrashOnOverflow(arrayBufferView);
3603 return arrayBufferView;
3604 }
3605#if ENABLE(WEB_CRYPTO)
3606 case CryptoKeyTag: {
3607 Vector<uint8_t> wrappedKey;
3608 if (!read(wrappedKey)) {
3609 fail();
3610 return JSValue();
3611 }
3612 Vector<uint8_t> serializedKey;
3613 if (!unwrapCryptoKey(m_lexicalGlobalObject, wrappedKey, serializedKey)) {
3614 fail();
3615 return JSValue();
3616 }
3617 JSValue cryptoKey;
3618 Vector<RefPtr<MessagePort>> dummyMessagePorts;
3619 CloneDeserializer rawKeyDeserializer(m_lexicalGlobalObject, m_globalObject, dummyMessagePorts, nullptr, { }, serializedKey);
3620 if (!rawKeyDeserializer.readCryptoKey(cryptoKey)) {
3621 fail();
3622 return JSValue();
3623 }
3624 m_gcBuffer.appendWithCrashOnOverflow(cryptoKey);
3625 return cryptoKey;
3626 }
3627#endif
3628 case DOMPointReadOnlyTag:
3629 return readDOMPoint<DOMPointReadOnly>();
3630 case DOMPointTag:
3631 return readDOMPoint<DOMPoint>();
3632 case DOMRectReadOnlyTag:
3633 return readDOMRect<DOMRectReadOnly>();
3634 case DOMRectTag:
3635 return readDOMRect<DOMRect>();
3636 case DOMMatrixReadOnlyTag:
3637 return readDOMMatrix<DOMMatrixReadOnly>();
3638 case DOMMatrixTag:
3639 return readDOMMatrix<DOMMatrix>();
3640 case DOMQuadTag:
3641 return readDOMQuad();
3642 case ImageBitmapTransferTag:
3643 return readTransferredImageBitmap();
3644#if ENABLE(WEB_RTC)
3645 case RTCCertificateTag:
3646 return readRTCCertificate();
3647
3648#endif
3649 case ImageBitmapTag:
3650 return readImageBitmap();
3651#if ENABLE(OFFSCREEN_CANVAS_IN_WORKERS)
3652 case OffscreenCanvasTransferTag:
3653 return readOffscreenCanvas();
3654#endif
3655#if ENABLE(WEB_RTC)
3656 case RTCDataChannelTransferTag:
3657 return readRTCDataChannel();
3658#endif
3659 case DOMExceptionTag:
3660 return readDOMException();
3661
3662 default:
3663 m_ptr--; // Push the tag back
3664 return JSValue();
3665 }
3666 }
3667
3668 template<SerializationTag Tag>
3669 bool consumeCollectionDataTerminationIfPossible()
3670 {
3671 if (readTag() == Tag)
3672 return true;
3673 m_ptr--;
3674 return false;
3675 }
3676
3677 JSGlobalObject* m_globalObject;
3678 bool m_isDOMGlobalObject;
3679 bool m_canCreateDOMObject;
3680 const uint8_t* m_ptr;
3681 const uint8_t* m_end;
3682 unsigned m_version;
3683 Vector<CachedString> m_constantPool;
3684 const Vector<RefPtr<MessagePort>>& m_messagePorts;
3685 ArrayBufferContentsArray* m_arrayBufferContents;
3686 Vector<RefPtr<JSC::ArrayBuffer>> m_arrayBuffers;
3687 Vector<String> m_blobURLs;
3688 Vector<String> m_blobFilePaths;
3689 ArrayBufferContentsArray* m_sharedBuffers;
3690 Vector<std::optional<ImageBitmapBacking>> m_backingStores;
3691 Vector<RefPtr<ImageBitmap>> m_imageBitmaps;
3692#if ENABLE(OFFSCREEN_CANVAS_IN_WORKERS)
3693 Vector<std::unique_ptr<DetachedOffscreenCanvas>> m_detachedOffscreenCanvases;
3694 Vector<RefPtr<OffscreenCanvas>> m_offscreenCanvases;
3695#endif
3696#if ENABLE(WEB_RTC)
3697 Vector<std::unique_ptr<DetachedRTCDataChannel>> m_detachedRTCDataChannels;
3698 Vector<RefPtr<RTCDataChannel>> m_rtcDataChannels;
3699#endif
3700#if ENABLE(WEBASSEMBLY)
3701 WasmModuleArray* m_wasmModules;
3702 WasmMemoryHandleArray* m_wasmMemoryHandles;
3703#endif
3704
3705 String blobFilePathForBlobURL(const String& blobURL)
3706 {
3707 size_t i = 0;
3708 for (; i < m_blobURLs.size(); ++i) {
3709 if (m_blobURLs[i] == blobURL)
3710 break;
3711 }
3712
3713 return i < m_blobURLs.size() ? m_blobFilePaths[i] : String();
3714 }
3715};
3716
3717DeserializationResult CloneDeserializer::deserialize()
3718{
3719 VM& vm = m_lexicalGlobalObject->vm();
3720 auto scope = DECLARE_THROW_SCOPE(vm);
3721
3722 Vector<uint32_t, 16> indexStack;
3723 Vector<Identifier, 16> propertyNameStack;
3724 Vector<JSObject*, 32> outputObjectStack;
3725 Vector<JSValue, 4> mapKeyStack;
3726 Vector<JSMap*, 4> mapStack;
3727 Vector<JSSet*, 4> setStack;
3728 Vector<WalkerState, 16> stateStack;
3729 WalkerState lexicalGlobalObject = StateUnknown;
3730 JSValue outValue;
3731
3732 while (1) {
3733 switch (lexicalGlobalObject) {
3734 arrayStartState:
3735 case ArrayStartState: {
3736 uint32_t length;
3737 if (!read(length)) {
3738 fail();
3739 goto error;
3740 }
3741 JSArray* outArray = constructEmptyArray(m_globalObject, static_cast<JSC::ArrayAllocationProfile*>(nullptr), length);
3742 if (UNLIKELY(scope.exception()))
3743 goto error;
3744 m_gcBuffer.appendWithCrashOnOverflow(outArray);
3745 outputObjectStack.append(outArray);
3746 }
3747 arrayStartVisitMember:
3748 FALLTHROUGH;
3749 case ArrayStartVisitMember: {
3750 uint32_t index;
3751 if (!read(index)) {
3752 fail();
3753 goto error;
3754 }
3755 if (index == TerminatorTag) {
3756 JSObject* outArray = outputObjectStack.last();
3757 outValue = outArray;
3758 outputObjectStack.removeLast();
3759 break;
3760 } else if (index == NonIndexPropertiesTag) {
3761 goto objectStartVisitMember;
3762 }
3763
3764 if (JSValue terminal = readTerminal()) {
3765 putProperty(outputObjectStack.last(), index, terminal);
3766 goto arrayStartVisitMember;
3767 }
3768 if (m_failed)
3769 goto error;
3770 indexStack.append(index);
3771 stateStack.append(ArrayEndVisitMember);
3772 goto stateUnknown;
3773 }
3774 case ArrayEndVisitMember: {
3775 JSObject* outArray = outputObjectStack.last();
3776 putProperty(outArray, indexStack.last(), outValue);
3777 indexStack.removeLast();
3778 goto arrayStartVisitMember;
3779 }
3780 objectStartState:
3781 case ObjectStartState: {
3782 if (outputObjectStack.size() > maximumFilterRecursion)
3783 return std::make_pair(JSValue(), SerializationReturnCode::StackOverflowError);
3784 JSObject* outObject = constructEmptyObject(m_lexicalGlobalObject, m_globalObject->objectPrototype());
3785 m_gcBuffer.appendWithCrashOnOverflow(outObject);
3786 outputObjectStack.append(outObject);
3787 }
3788 objectStartVisitMember:
3789 FALLTHROUGH;
3790 case ObjectStartVisitMember: {
3791 CachedStringRef cachedString;
3792 bool wasTerminator = false;
3793 if (!readStringData(cachedString, wasTerminator)) {
3794 if (!wasTerminator)
3795 goto error;
3796
3797 JSObject* outObject = outputObjectStack.last();
3798 outValue = outObject;
3799 outputObjectStack.removeLast();
3800 break;
3801 }
3802
3803 if (JSValue terminal = readTerminal()) {
3804 putProperty(outputObjectStack.last(), Identifier::fromString(vm, cachedString->string()), terminal);
3805 goto objectStartVisitMember;
3806 }
3807 stateStack.append(ObjectEndVisitMember);
3808 propertyNameStack.append(Identifier::fromString(vm, cachedString->string()));
3809 goto stateUnknown;
3810 }
3811 case ObjectEndVisitMember: {
3812 putProperty(outputObjectStack.last(), propertyNameStack.last(), outValue);
3813 propertyNameStack.removeLast();
3814 goto objectStartVisitMember;
3815 }
3816 mapObjectStartState: {
3817 if (outputObjectStack.size() > maximumFilterRecursion)
3818 return std::make_pair(JSValue(), SerializationReturnCode::StackOverflowError);
3819 JSMap* map = JSMap::create(m_lexicalGlobalObject, m_lexicalGlobalObject->vm(), m_globalObject->mapStructure());
3820 if (UNLIKELY(scope.exception()))
3821 goto error;
3822 m_gcBuffer.appendWithCrashOnOverflow(map);
3823 outputObjectStack.append(map);
3824 mapStack.append(map);
3825 goto mapDataStartVisitEntry;
3826 }
3827 mapDataStartVisitEntry:
3828 case MapDataStartVisitEntry: {
3829 if (consumeCollectionDataTerminationIfPossible<NonMapPropertiesTag>()) {
3830 mapStack.removeLast();
3831 goto objectStartVisitMember;
3832 }
3833 stateStack.append(MapDataEndVisitKey);
3834 goto stateUnknown;
3835 }
3836 case MapDataEndVisitKey: {
3837 mapKeyStack.append(outValue);
3838 stateStack.append(MapDataEndVisitValue);
3839 goto stateUnknown;
3840 }
3841 case MapDataEndVisitValue: {
3842 mapStack.last()->set(m_lexicalGlobalObject, mapKeyStack.last(), outValue);
3843 mapKeyStack.removeLast();
3844 goto mapDataStartVisitEntry;
3845 }
3846
3847 setObjectStartState: {
3848 if (outputObjectStack.size() > maximumFilterRecursion)
3849 return std::make_pair(JSValue(), SerializationReturnCode::StackOverflowError);
3850 JSSet* set = JSSet::create(m_lexicalGlobalObject, m_lexicalGlobalObject->vm(), m_globalObject->setStructure());
3851 if (UNLIKELY(scope.exception()))
3852 goto error;
3853 m_gcBuffer.appendWithCrashOnOverflow(set);
3854 outputObjectStack.append(set);
3855 setStack.append(set);
3856 goto setDataStartVisitEntry;
3857 }
3858 setDataStartVisitEntry:
3859 case SetDataStartVisitEntry: {
3860 if (consumeCollectionDataTerminationIfPossible<NonSetPropertiesTag>()) {
3861 setStack.removeLast();
3862 goto objectStartVisitMember;
3863 }
3864 stateStack.append(SetDataEndVisitKey);
3865 goto stateUnknown;
3866 }
3867 case SetDataEndVisitKey: {
3868 JSSet* set = setStack.last();
3869 set->add(m_lexicalGlobalObject, outValue);
3870 goto setDataStartVisitEntry;
3871 }
3872
3873 stateUnknown:
3874 case StateUnknown:
3875 if (JSValue terminal = readTerminal()) {
3876 outValue = terminal;
3877 break;
3878 }
3879 SerializationTag tag = readTag();
3880 if (tag == ArrayTag)
3881 goto arrayStartState;
3882 if (tag == ObjectTag)
3883 goto objectStartState;
3884 if (tag == MapObjectTag)
3885 goto mapObjectStartState;
3886 if (tag == SetObjectTag)
3887 goto setObjectStartState;
3888 goto error;
3889 }
3890 if (stateStack.isEmpty())
3891 break;
3892
3893 lexicalGlobalObject = stateStack.last();
3894 stateStack.removeLast();
3895 }
3896 ASSERT(outValue);
3897 ASSERT(!m_failed);
3898 return std::make_pair(outValue, SerializationReturnCode::SuccessfullyCompleted);
3899error:
3900 fail();
3901 return std::make_pair(JSValue(), SerializationReturnCode::ValidationError);
3902}

3927#if ENABLE(OFFSCREEN_CANVAS_IN_WORKERS)
3928 , Vector<std::unique_ptr<DetachedOffscreenCanvas>>&& detachedOffscreenCanvases
3929#endif
3930#if ENABLE(WEB_RTC)
3931 , Vector<std::unique_ptr<DetachedRTCDataChannel>>&& detachedRTCDataChannels
3932#endif
3933#if ENABLE(WEBASSEMBLY)
3934 , std::unique_ptr<WasmModuleArray> wasmModulesArray
3935 , std::unique_ptr<WasmMemoryHandleArray> wasmMemoryHandlesArray
3936#endif
3937 )
3938 : m_data(WTFMove(buffer))
3939 , m_arrayBufferContentsArray(WTFMove(arrayBufferContentsArray))
3940 , m_sharedBufferContentsArray(WTFMove(sharedBufferContentsArray))
3941 , m_backingStores(WTFMove(backingStores))
3942#if ENABLE(OFFSCREEN_CANVAS_IN_WORKERS)
3943 , m_detachedOffscreenCanvases(WTFMove(detachedOffscreenCanvases))
3944#endif
3945#if ENABLE(WEB_RTC)
3946 , m_detachedRTCDataChannels(WTFMove(detachedRTCDataChannels))
3947#endif
3948#if ENABLE(WEBASSEMBLY)
3949 , m_wasmModulesArray(WTFMove(wasmModulesArray))
3950 , m_wasmMemoryHandlesArray(WTFMove(wasmMemoryHandlesArray))
3951#endif
3952{
3953 // Since this SerializedScriptValue is meant to be passed between threads, its String data members
3954 // need to be isolatedCopies so we don't run into thread safety issues for the StringImpls.
3955 m_blobURLs.reserveInitialCapacity(blobURLs.size());
3956 for (auto& url : blobURLs)
3957 m_blobURLs.uncheckedAppend(url.isolatedCopy());
3958 m_memoryCost = computeMemoryCost();
3959}
3960
3961size_t SerializedScriptValue::computeMemoryCost() const
3962{
3963 size_t cost = m_data.size();
3964
3965 if (m_arrayBufferContentsArray) {
3966 for (auto& content : *m_arrayBufferContentsArray)
3967 cost += content.sizeInBytes();
3968 }
3969
3970 if (m_sharedBufferContentsArray) {
3971 for (auto& content : *m_sharedBufferContentsArray)
3972 cost += content.sizeInBytes();
3973 }
3974
3975 for (auto& backingStore : m_backingStores) {
3976 if (auto buffer = backingStore ? backingStore->buffer() : nullptr)
3977 cost += buffer->memoryCost();
3978 }
3979
3980#if ENABLE(OFFSCREEN_CANVAS_IN_WORKERS)
3981 for (auto& canvas : m_detachedOffscreenCanvases) {
3982 if (canvas)
3983 cost += canvas->memoryCost();
3984 }
3985#endif
3986#if ENABLE(WEB_RTC)
3987 for (auto& channel : m_detachedRTCDataChannels) {
3988 if (channel)
3989 cost += channel->memoryCost();
3990 }
3991#endif
3992
3993#if ENABLE(WEBASSEMBLY)
3994 // We are not supporting WebAssembly Module memory estimation yet.
3995 if (m_wasmMemoryHandlesArray) {
3996 for (auto& content : *m_wasmMemoryHandlesArray)
3997 cost += content->size();
3998 }
3999#endif
4000
4001 for (auto& urls : m_blobURLs)
4002 cost += urls.sizeInBytes();
4003
4004 return cost;
4005}
4006
4007static ExceptionOr<std::unique_ptr<ArrayBufferContentsArray>> transferArrayBuffers(VM& vm, const Vector<RefPtr<JSC::ArrayBuffer>>& arrayBuffers)
4008{
4009 if (arrayBuffers.isEmpty())
4010 return nullptr;
4011
4012 auto contents = makeUnique<ArrayBufferContentsArray>(arrayBuffers.size());
4013
4014 HashSet<JSC::ArrayBuffer*> visited;
4015 for (size_t arrayBufferIndex = 0; arrayBufferIndex < arrayBuffers.size(); arrayBufferIndex++) {
4016 if (visited.contains(arrayBuffers[arrayBufferIndex].get()))
4017 continue;
4018 visited.add(arrayBuffers[arrayBufferIndex].get());
4019
4020 bool result = arrayBuffers[arrayBufferIndex]->transferTo(vm, contents->at(arrayBufferIndex));
4021 if (!result)
4022 return Exception { TypeError };
4023 }
4024
4025 return contents;
4026}
4027
4028static void maybeThrowExceptionIfSerializationFailed(JSGlobalObject& lexicalGlobalObject, SerializationReturnCode code)
4029{
4030 auto& vm = lexicalGlobalObject.vm();
4031 auto scope = DECLARE_THROW_SCOPE(vm);
4032
4033 switch (code) {
4034 case SerializationReturnCode::SuccessfullyCompleted:
4035 break;
4036 case SerializationReturnCode::StackOverflowError:
4037 throwException(&lexicalGlobalObject, scope, createStackOverflowError(&lexicalGlobalObject));
4038 break;
4039 case SerializationReturnCode::ValidationError:
4040 throwTypeError(&lexicalGlobalObject, scope, "Unable to deserialize data."_s);
4041 break;
4042 case SerializationReturnCode::DataCloneError:
4043 throwDataCloneError(lexicalGlobalObject, scope);
4044 break;
4045 case SerializationReturnCode::ExistingExceptionError:
4046 case SerializationReturnCode::UnspecifiedError:
4047 break;
4048 case SerializationReturnCode::InterruptedExecutionError:
4049 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
4050 }
4051}
4052
4053static Exception exceptionForSerializationFailure(SerializationReturnCode code)
4054{
4055 ASSERT(code != SerializationReturnCode::SuccessfullyCompleted);
4056
4057 switch (code) {
4058 case SerializationReturnCode::StackOverflowError:
4059 return Exception { StackOverflowError };
4060 case SerializationReturnCode::ValidationError:
4061 return Exception { TypeError };
4062 case SerializationReturnCode::DataCloneError:
4063 return Exception { DataCloneError };
4064 case SerializationReturnCode::ExistingExceptionError:
4065 return Exception { ExistingExceptionError };
4066 case SerializationReturnCode::UnspecifiedError:
4067 return Exception { TypeError };
4068 case SerializationReturnCode::SuccessfullyCompleted:
4069 case SerializationReturnCode::InterruptedExecutionError:
4070 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
4071 return Exception { TypeError };
4072 }
4073 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
4074 return Exception { TypeError };
4075}
4076
4077RefPtr<SerializedScriptValue> SerializedScriptValue::create(JSGlobalObject& lexicalGlobalObject, JSValue value, SerializationErrorMode throwExceptions)
4078{
4079 Vector<uint8_t> buffer;
4080 Vector<String> blobURLs;
4081 Vector<RefPtr<MessagePort>> dummyMessagePorts;
4082 Vector<RefPtr<ImageBitmap>> dummyImageBitmaps;
4083#if ENABLE(OFFSCREEN_CANVAS_IN_WORKERS)
4084 Vector<RefPtr<OffscreenCanvas>> dummyOffscreenCanvases;
4085#endif
4086#if ENABLE(WEB_RTC)
4087 Vector<Ref<RTCDataChannel>> dummyRTCDataChannels;
4088#endif
4089 Vector<RefPtr<JSC::ArrayBuffer>> dummyArrayBuffers;
4090#if ENABLE(WEBASSEMBLY)
4091 WasmModuleArray dummyModules;
4092 WasmMemoryHandleArray dummyMemoryHandles;
4093#endif
4094 ArrayBufferContentsArray dummySharedBuffers;
4095 auto code = CloneSerializer::serialize(&lexicalGlobalObject, value, dummyMessagePorts, dummyArrayBuffers, dummyImageBitmaps,
4096#if ENABLE(OFFSCREEN_CANVAS_IN_WORKERS)
4097 dummyOffscreenCanvases,
4098#endif
4099#if ENABLE(WEB_RTC)
4100 dummyRTCDataChannels,
4101#endif
4102#if ENABLE(WEBASSEMBLY)
4103 dummyModules,
4104 dummyMemoryHandles,
4105#endif
4106 blobURLs, buffer, SerializationContext::Default, dummySharedBuffers);
4107
4108#if ENABLE(WEBASSEMBLY)
4109 ASSERT_WITH_MESSAGE(dummyModules.isEmpty(), "Wasm::Module serialization is only allowed in the postMessage context");
4110 ASSERT_WITH_MESSAGE(dummyMemoryHandles.isEmpty(), "Wasm::Memory serialization is only allowed in the postMessage context");
4111#endif
4112
4113 if (throwExceptions == SerializationErrorMode::Throwing)
4114 maybeThrowExceptionIfSerializationFailed(lexicalGlobalObject, code);
4115
4116 if (code != SerializationReturnCode::SuccessfullyCompleted)
4117 return nullptr;
4118
4119 return adoptRef(*new SerializedScriptValue(WTFMove(buffer), blobURLs, nullptr, nullptr, { }));
4120}
4121
4122static bool containsDuplicates(const Vector<RefPtr<ImageBitmap>>& imageBitmaps)
4123{
4124 HashSet<ImageBitmap*> visited;
4125 for (auto& imageBitmap : imageBitmaps) {
4126 if (!visited.add(imageBitmap.get()))
4127 return true;
4128 }
4129 return false;
4130}
4131
4132#if ENABLE(OFFSCREEN_CANVAS_IN_WORKERS)
4133static bool canOffscreenCanvasesDetach(const Vector<RefPtr<OffscreenCanvas>>& offscreenCanvases)
4134{
4135 HashSet<OffscreenCanvas*> visited;
4136 for (auto& offscreenCanvas : offscreenCanvases) {
4137 if (!offscreenCanvas->canDetach())
4138 return false;
4139 // Check the return value of add, we should not encounter duplicates.
4140 if (!visited.add(offscreenCanvas.get()))
4141 return false;
4142 }
4143 return true;
4144}
4145#endif
4146
4147#if ENABLE(WEB_RTC)
4148static bool canDetachRTCDataChannels(const Vector<Ref<RTCDataChannel>>& channels)
4149{
4150 HashSet<RTCDataChannel*> visited;
4151 for (auto& channel : channels) {
4152 if (!channel->canDetach())
4153 return false;
4154 // Check the return value of add, we should not encounter duplicates.
4155 if (!visited.add(channel.ptr()))
4156 return false;
4157 }
4158 return true;
4159}
4160#endif

4162ExceptionOr<Ref<SerializedScriptValue>> SerializedScriptValue::create(JSGlobalObject& lexicalGlobalObject, JSValue value, Vector<JSC::Strong<JSC::JSObject>>&& transferList, Vector<RefPtr<MessagePort>>& messagePorts, SerializationContext context)
4163{
4164 VM& vm = lexicalGlobalObject.vm();
4165 Vector<RefPtr<JSC::ArrayBuffer>> arrayBuffers;
4166 Vector<RefPtr<ImageBitmap>> imageBitmaps;
4167#if ENABLE(OFFSCREEN_CANVAS_IN_WORKERS)
4168 Vector<RefPtr<OffscreenCanvas>> offscreenCanvases;
4169#endif
4170#if ENABLE(WEB_RTC)
4171 Vector<Ref<RTCDataChannel>> dataChannels;
4172#endif
4173 for (auto& transferable : transferList) {
4174 if (auto arrayBuffer = toPossiblySharedArrayBuffer(vm, transferable.get())) {
4175 if (arrayBuffer->isDetached() || arrayBuffer->isShared())
4176 return Exception { DataCloneError };
4177 if (arrayBuffer->isLocked()) {
4178 auto scope = DECLARE_THROW_SCOPE(vm);
4179 throwVMTypeError(&lexicalGlobalObject, scope, errorMesasgeForTransfer(arrayBuffer));
4180 return Exception { ExistingExceptionError };
4181 }
4182 arrayBuffers.append(WTFMove(arrayBuffer));
4183 continue;
4184 }
4185 if (auto port = JSMessagePort::toWrapped(vm, transferable.get())) {
4186 // FIXME: This should check if the port is detached as per https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/infrastructure.html#istransferable.
4187 messagePorts.append(WTFMove(port));
4188 continue;
4189 }
4190
4191 if (auto imageBitmap = JSImageBitmap::toWrapped(vm, transferable.get())) {
4192 if (imageBitmap->isDetached())
4193 return Exception { DataCloneError };
4194
4195 imageBitmaps.append(WTFMove(imageBitmap));
4196 continue;
4197 }
4198
4199#if ENABLE(OFFSCREEN_CANVAS_IN_WORKERS)
4200 if (auto offscreenCanvas = JSOffscreenCanvas::toWrapped(vm, transferable.get())) {
4201 offscreenCanvases.append(WTFMove(offscreenCanvas));
4202 continue;
4203 }
4204#endif
4205
4206#if ENABLE(WEB_RTC)
4207 if (auto channel = JSRTCDataChannel::toWrapped(vm, transferable.get())) {
4208 dataChannels.append(*channel);
4209 continue;
4210 }
4211#endif
4212
4213 return Exception { DataCloneError };
4214 }
4215
4216 if (containsDuplicates(imageBitmaps))
4217 return Exception { DataCloneError };
4218#if ENABLE(OFFSCREEN_CANVAS_IN_WORKERS)
4219 if (!canOffscreenCanvasesDetach(offscreenCanvases))
4220 return Exception { InvalidStateError };
4221#endif
4222#if ENABLE(WEB_RTC)
4223 if (!canDetachRTCDataChannels(dataChannels))
4224 return Exception { DataCloneError };
4225#endif
4226
4227 Vector<uint8_t> buffer;
4228 Vector<String> blobURLs;
4229#if ENABLE(WEBASSEMBLY)
4230 WasmModuleArray wasmModules;
4231 WasmMemoryHandleArray wasmMemoryHandles;
4232#endif
4233 std::unique_ptr<ArrayBufferContentsArray> sharedBuffers = makeUnique<ArrayBufferContentsArray>();
4234 auto code = CloneSerializer::serialize(&lexicalGlobalObject, value, messagePorts, arrayBuffers, imageBitmaps,
4235#if ENABLE(OFFSCREEN_CANVAS_IN_WORKERS)
4236 offscreenCanvases,
4237#endif
4238#if ENABLE(WEB_RTC)
4239 dataChannels,
4240#endif
4241#if ENABLE(WEBASSEMBLY)
4242 wasmModules,
4243 wasmMemoryHandles,
4244#endif
4245 blobURLs, buffer, context, *sharedBuffers);
4246
4247 if (code != SerializationReturnCode::SuccessfullyCompleted)
4248 return exceptionForSerializationFailure(code);
4249
4250 auto arrayBufferContentsArray = transferArrayBuffers(vm, arrayBuffers);
4251 if (arrayBufferContentsArray.hasException())
4252 return arrayBufferContentsArray.releaseException();
4253
4254 auto backingStores = ImageBitmap::detachBitmaps(WTFMove(imageBitmaps));
4255
4256#if ENABLE(OFFSCREEN_CANVAS_IN_WORKERS)
4257 Vector<std::unique_ptr<DetachedOffscreenCanvas>> detachedCanvases;
4258 for (auto offscreenCanvas : offscreenCanvases)
4259 detachedCanvases.append(offscreenCanvas->detach());
4260#endif
4261#if ENABLE(WEB_RTC)
4262 Vector<std::unique_ptr<DetachedRTCDataChannel>> detachedRTCDataChannels;
4263 for (auto& channel : dataChannels)
4264 detachedRTCDataChannels.append(channel->detach());
4265#endif
4266
4267 return adoptRef(*new SerializedScriptValue(WTFMove(buffer), blobURLs, arrayBufferContentsArray.releaseReturnValue(), context == SerializationContext::WorkerPostMessage ? WTFMove(sharedBuffers) : nullptr, WTFMove(backingStores)
4268#if ENABLE(OFFSCREEN_CANVAS_IN_WORKERS)
4269 , WTFMove(detachedCanvases)
4270#endif
4271#if ENABLE(WEB_RTC)
4272 , WTFMove(detachedRTCDataChannels)
4273#endif
4274#if ENABLE(WEBASSEMBLY)
4275 , makeUnique<WasmModuleArray>(wasmModules)
4276 , context == SerializationContext::WorkerPostMessage ? makeUnique<WasmMemoryHandleArray>(wasmMemoryHandles) : nullptr
4277#endif
4278 ));
4279}

4289RefPtr<SerializedScriptValue> SerializedScriptValue::create(JSContextRef originContext, JSValueRef apiValue, JSValueRef* exception)
4290{
4291 JSGlobalObject* lexicalGlobalObject = toJS(originContext);
4292 VM& vm = lexicalGlobalObject->vm();
4293 JSLockHolder locker(vm);
4294 auto scope = DECLARE_CATCH_SCOPE(vm);
4295
4296 JSValue value = toJS(lexicalGlobalObject, apiValue);
4297 auto serializedValue = SerializedScriptValue::create(*lexicalGlobalObject, value);
4298 if (UNLIKELY(scope.exception())) {
4299 if (exception)
4300 *exception = toRef(lexicalGlobalObject, scope.exception()->value());
4301 scope.clearException();
4302 return nullptr;
4303 }
4304 ASSERT(serializedValue);
4305 return serializedValue;
4306}

4335#if ENABLE(WEBASSEMBLY)

4383void SerializedScriptValue::writeBlobsToDiskForIndexedDB(CompletionHandler<void(IDBValue&&)>&& completionHandler)
4384{
4385 ASSERT(isMainThread());
4386 ASSERT(hasBlobURLs());
4387
4388 blobRegistry().writeBlobsToTemporaryFiles(m_blobURLs, [completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler), this, protectedThis = makeRef(*this)] (auto&& blobFilePaths) mutable {
4389 ASSERT(isMainThread());
4390
4391 if (blobFilePaths.isEmpty()) {
4392 // We should have successfully written blobs to temporary files.
4393 // If we failed, then we can't successfully store this record.
4394 completionHandler({ });
4395 return;
4396 }
4397
4398 ASSERT(m_blobURLs.size() == blobFilePaths.size());
4399
4400 completionHandler({ *this, m_blobURLs, blobFilePaths });
4401 });
4402}
4403
4404IDBValue SerializedScriptValue::writeBlobsToDiskForIndexedDBSynchronously()
4405{
4406 ASSERT(!isMainThread());
4407
4408 BinarySemaphore semaphore;
4409 IDBValue value;
4410 callOnMainThread([this, &semaphore, &value] {
4411 writeBlobsToDiskForIndexedDB([&semaphore, &value](IDBValue&& result) {
4412 ASSERT(isMainThread());
4413 value.setAsIsolatedCopy(result);
4414
4415 semaphore.signal();
4416 });
4417 });
4418 semaphore.wait();
4419
4420 return value;
4421}
